      <h1 class="font-manrope text-sm">Seksjon 2</h1>
      <p class="text-3xl p-10">
        With Into the Woods, Ordrupgaard proudly presents Flora Yukhnovich in
        her first museum exhibition outside the UK. Known for her rising
        prominence in the art world, Yukhnovich brings together Rococo-inspired
        aesthetics and a modern sensibility that blurs the boundaries between
        fine art and popular culture. The exhibition invites visitors into a
        fantastical, enchanted forest where the conscious and unconscious meet.
        Here, historical and contemporary references intertwine—from classical
        figures like Venus to modern icons such as Nicki Minaj—with the female
        body serving as a central theme. Through her evocative visual language,
        Yukhnovich transcends traditional genre boundaries, offering an
        immersive and thought-provoking experience.
      </p>
